TopicTitle: KSP CTDing without errors in the log

Articles.Content:
Hello everyone !

I'm managing my game instances and installing mods through CKAN, so i have 2 instances, KSP 1.10.1 and KSP 1.12.2 and the 1.10 is working ok, but the 1.12 with a similar mod set is CDTing without errors in the log i tried deleting the save and recreating it to no avail. The game launches, patches are applied and the whole thing works perfectly untill the game itself starts loading, then it hangs and crashes.

This is a rather light mod list so here it goes:
